ehavioral health and chronic disease management solutions that improve health and financial outcomes sandi is responsible for the johnson  johnson consumerfacing businesses including the consumer family of companies and the consumer medical device businesses johnson  johnson vision care and johnson  johnson diabetes care these businesses generate approximately  billion in revenue and include iconic brands such as johnson’s baby® neutrogena® listerine® tylenol® clean  clear® acuvue® onetouch® and bandaid® johnson  johnson’s consumer group was the fastest growing consumer packaged goods business in the united states in  before joining johnson  johnson sandi was chairman  ceo of bayer cropscience ag in germany she had previously served as ceo of bayer medical care and president of bayer healthcare ag’s diabetes care division earlier sandi held leadership roles at medco health solutions previously known as merckmedco nabisco whirlpool corporation and mckinsey and company inc sandi holds a ba from cornell university and an mpa from princeton university she is a member of the board of directors of microsoft and formerly on the board of directors of the dun  bradstreet corporation where she chaired the innovation  technology committee sandi was a founding member of women corporate directors she is a member of women’s forum and c she serves on the rutberg  company wireless influencers  board of advisors and the international advisory board of the center for the advanced study of india university of pennsylvania sandi is a member of the board of trustees institute of advanced study one of the world’s leading centers for theoretical research and intellectual inquiry she was also chairman of the board of ecohealth alliance sandi has been named to fortune magazine’s list of the most powerful women three times most recently being the  list management team board of directors management team alex gorsky chairman board of directors and chief executive officer dominic j caruso joaquin duato peter fasolo phd jorge mesquita sandra e peterson michael sneed paul stoffels md michael ullmann kathryn e wengel board of directors alex gorsky chairman board of directors and chief executive officer mary c beckerle d scott davis ian e l davis mark b mcclellan anne m mulcahy william d perez charles prince a eugene washington ronald a williams sandra e peterson  working mother skip to main content subscribe subscribe sandra e peterson group worldwide chairman  johnson  johnson posted nov th  at pm comments sandra e peterson sandra e peterson is group worldwide chairman johnson  johnson and member of the company’s executive committee she has responsibility for the consumer group of companies information technology and global supply chain prior to joining the company in december  she had an extensive global career in life sciences consumer goods and consulting sandi previously served as chair and ceo of bayer cropscience ag based in europe a role she assumed in  after serving as president and ceo of bayer medical care and president of bayer healthcare ag’s diabetes care prior to joining bayer in  peterson spent five years in leadership roles at medco health solutions formerly merckmedco she also led global research and development procurement and regulatory affairs at nabisco inc and strategy finance and product development at whirlpool corporation she began her career in consulting with mckinsey  company inc a graduate of cornell university with a ba in government sandi also holds an mpa in applied economics from princeton university she is a member of the board of directors of the dun  bradstreet corporation tags the  nafe women of excellence awards speaker view the discussion thread latest more career sandra e peterson executive profile  biography  bloomberg july    am et pharmaceuticals company overview of johnson  johnson snapshotpeople  overviewboard memberscommittees executive profile sandra e peterson executive vice president and group worldwide chair